  },
  {
    title: "",
    letter: `There‚Äôs no day when I don‚Äôt thank God for giving me <i>you</i>.<br>
      You are my person, my peace, and my chaos ‚Äî all at once.<br>
      You're not just beautiful ‚Äî you're trouble.<br>
      Because every time I think of you, I smile like an idiot.`,
    signature: ""
  },
  {
    title: "",
    letter: `<div class="quote">
        "I‚Äôm the one who hears only your voice even in the loudest noise of the world, and you‚Äôre the one whose single video lights up the loneliness of my nights. When you pout in your own little way, like an adorably angry fairy, you still look like the most beautiful thing my eyes have ever seen."
      </div>
      Maybe that‚Äôs why, when you walk down a path that brings me pain, my heart doesn‚Äôt just break‚Ä¶ it shatters.<br>
      You‚Äôve become more than just my reality ‚Äî you‚Äôre the story my soul lives in now.`,
    signature: ""
  },
  {
    title: "",
    letter: `When you go against me, it feels like my own world is turning its back on me.<br>
      But the truth is, I only get upset because you are mine.<br>
      You are my smile, the happiness of my soul, and the light in the darkness of my nights.<br>
      I just want you to understand‚Ä¶ the ones we love the most, they are the ones who can hurt us the deepest.`,
    signature: ""
  },
  {
    title: "",
    letter: `But even that pain doesn‚Äôt matter‚Ä¶ because you matter more.<br>
      Always, mera bacha üíûüòò.<br>
      <div class="quote">‚ÄúYou are my everything.‚Äù</div>`,
    signature: `I love you ‚ù§Ô∏è<br>‚Äì Aapka [AMMAR]`
  }
];

const loveTitle = document.getElementById('love-title');
const loveLetter = document.getElementById('love-letter');
const signature = document.getElementById('signature');
const navPrev = document.getElementById('prev-btn');
const navNext = document.getElementById('next-btn');
const pageIndicator = document.getElementById('page-indicator');
let currentPage = 0;

function showPage(idx) {
  currentPage = idx;
  loveTitle.innerHTML = pages[idx].title || "";
  loveLetter.innerHTML = pages[idx].letter;
  signature.innerHTML = pages[idx].signature || "";
  navPrev.style.display = (idx === 0) ? 'none' : '';
  navNext.style.display = (idx === pages.length-1) ? 'none' : '';
  pageIndicator.innerHTML = `Page ${idx+1} / ${pages.length}`;
}

navPrev.onclick = ()=>showPage(Math.max(0,currentPage-1));
navNext.onclick = ()=>showPage(Math.min(pages.length-1,currentPage+1));
// Mobile tap
loveLetter.onclick = ()=>{if (currentPage<pages.length-1) navNext.click();}
loveTitle.onclick = ()=>{if (currentPage<pages.length-1) navNext.click();}
signature.onclick = ()=>{if (currentPage<pages.length-1) navNext.click();}
window.addEventListener('keydown', (e)=>{
  if (e.key==='ArrowRight' || e.key==='d') navNext.click();
  if (e.key==='ArrowLeft' || e.key==='a') navPrev.click();
});
// Swipe navigation for mobile
let touchStartX = null;
document.getElementById('love-card').addEventListener('touchstart', e=>{
  if (e.touches.length===1) touchStartX = e.touches[0].clientX;
});
document.getElementById('love-card').addEventListener('touchend', e=>{
  if (touchStartX!==null) {
    let dx = e.changedTouches[0].clientX - touchStartX;
    if (dx < -40) navNext.click();
    else if (dx > 40) navPrev.click();
    touchStartX = null;
  }
});
showPage(0);
</script>
</body>
